# Ability Name			Category of Ability		Type						Required Deity		Multiple Requirements																			Required Race	Define						Description																																Bonus to skill			Modify VAR							Source Page
Flounderer				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait	PREDEITY:1,Zogmugot	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Flounderer],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait]			PRERACE:1,Goblin	DEFINE:FoundererHeldBreathDuration|0	DESC:You are adept at swimming and holding your breath. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Swim checks, and can hold your breath for %1 rounds before you risk drowning.|FoundererHeldBreathDuration		BONUS:SKILL|Swim|1|TYPE=Trait	BONUS:VAR|FoundererHeldBreathDuration|CON+3	SOURCEPAGE:pg.16
Mother's Teeth			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait	PREDEITY:1,Lamashtu	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Mother's Teeth],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait]		PRERACE:1,Goblin								DESC:Your teeth are more jagged and pointed than normal. You can make a bite attack for 1d2 points of damage as a secondary attack.																									SOURCEPAGE:pg.16
Restless Hunger			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait	PREDEITY:1,Venkelvore	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Restless Hunger],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait]		PRERACE:1,Goblin								DESC:If you have a piece of food (or something a goblin might consider food), you can quickly eat it as part of a charge attack once per day. Doing so increases your speed by 10 feet for 1 round.														SOURCEPAGE:pg.16
Strength of the Barghest	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait	PREDEITY:1,Hadregash	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Strength of the Barghest],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait]	PRERACE:1,Goblin								DESC:The blood of the barghests is strong in you. Once per day as a free action, you can gain a +2 trait bonus on any Strength check or Strength-based skill check.																			SOURCEPAGE:pg.16
Wolf Cub				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait	PREDEITY:1,Zarongel	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Wolf Cub],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait]			PRERACE:1,Goblin								DESC:Your body has clumps of ugly fur, a sure sign of wolf blood! You win! Once per day as a standard action, you can take a deep breath through your nose to gain the scent ability for 1 minute.														SOURCEPAGE:pg.16

